sys_ui_message.message: Once "Compute Interface.CreateNode" finishes execution, its JSON output will be parsed to look for 'nodeId' attribute, which is say 'us-west-1/i-06adfe8ef9309b5bb' and replaced into the Output Attributes. The Output Attributes will then look like this - {"NodeId":"us-west-1/i-06adfe8ef9309b5bb"}
